#: app/templates/about.html:10
msgid "About Grylli"
msgstr "About Grylli"

#: app/templates/about.html:13
msgid ""
"Grylli is a secure, self-hosted message delivery platform that automatically"
" sends pre-configured messages if a user fails to check in within a defined "
"time period."
msgstr ""
"Grylli dia sehatra fandefasan-kafatra azo antoka sy hosokajiana manokana "
"izay mandefa hafatra voaomana mialoha raha tsy mijery izy ny mpampiasa ao "
"anatin'ny fe-potoana voafaritra."

#: app/templates/about.html:14
msgid ""
"It supports multiple users, customizable schedules, and recurring reminders."
msgstr "Manohana mpampiasa maro sy fandaharam-potoana azo amboarina izy io."

#: app/templates/about.html:15
msgid ""
"Messages and reminders can be delivered via email, webhooks, or over 100 "
"third-party services through Apprise."
msgstr ""
"Afaka alefa amin'ny alalan'ny mailaka, webhooks, na serivisy avy amin'ny "
"antoko fahatelo efa mihoatra ny 80 izy ireo amin'ny alalan'i Apprise."

#: app/templates/about.html:16
msgid ""
"Users can configure their own SMTP servers to ensure emails and reminders "
"appear to come directly from them — not from the system administrator."
msgstr ""
"Afaka mametraka ny SMTP serivera azy manokana ny mpampiasa mba hahazoana "
"antoka fa ny hafatra dia toa mivantana avy aminy fa tsy avy amin'ny "
"mpiandraikitra ny rafitra."

#: app/templates/about.html:17
msgid ""
"Sensitive data is encrypted at rest, and all operations are secured with "
"strong authentication and audit-friendly logging."
msgstr ""
"Voaaro amin'ny fitahirizana ny tahirin-kevitra saro-pady, ary sehatra "
"rehetra mikasika ny hafatra dia voaaro amin'ny fisoratana anarana mafy sy "
"fofona anaovana fanamarinana."

#: app/templates/about.html:18
msgid ""
"Built with a modern, reactive technology stack, Grylli is optimized for "
"responsiveness and works seamlessly across desktop and mobile devices."
msgstr ""
"Noforonina amin'ny teknolojia mihetsiketsika maoderina, optimizena ho an'ny "
"valinteny haingana i Grylli ary miasa tsy misy sakantsakana manerana ny "
"fitaovana anaty birao sy finday."

#: app/templates/about.html:23
msgid "Version:"
msgstr "Version:"

#: app/templates/about.html:26
msgid "Repository:"
msgstr "Repository:"

#: app/templates/about.html:30
msgid "GitHub - samcro1967/grylli"
msgstr "GitHub - samcro1967/grylli"

