msgid ""
"Grylli includes built-in instructions throughout the app to help you "
"configure and manage your setup."
msgstr ""
"Misy torolalana tafiditra ao amin'ny fampiharana manontolo i Grylli mba "
"hanampy anao amin'ny fametrahana sy fitantanana."

#: app/templates/help.html:8
msgid ""
"This page provides an overview of key features and direct links to where "
"they can be managed."
msgstr ""
"Mitovy amin'ity pejy ity ny famintinana ny endri-javatra lehibe sy rohy "
"mivantana amin'izay azo tantanana."

