msgid "Emails"
msgstr "Mailaka"

#: app/templates/help.html:34
msgid "View and manage secure email messages"
msgstr "Topimaso momba ny hafatra email azo antoka"

#: app/templates/help.html:38
msgid "Security"
msgstr "🔐 Fiarovana"

#: app/templates/help.html:39
msgid "Grylli encrypts sensitive data and logs all key actions for auditing."
msgstr ""
"Manan-maso fo ny tahirin-kevitra saropady i Grylli ary mitahiry ny hetsika "
"lehibe rehetra ho an'ny fanamarinana."

#: app/templates/index.html:9 app/views/locale.py:95
msgid "Welcome to Grylli"
msgstr "Tonga soa ao Grylli"

#: app/templates/index.html:11
msgid "Pronounced"
msgstr "Lazaina"

#: app/templates/index.html:11
msgid "like “grill-ee”"
msgstr "toy ny \"grill-ee\""

#: app/templates/index.html:14
msgid ""
"Grylli is a secure message scheduling and delivery system designed to ensure"
" your important messages are delivered — even if you can’t be there to send "
"them."
msgstr ""
"Grylli dia rafitra fandefasana sy fandaminana hafatra azo antoka natao "
"hanampy antoka fa alefa ireo hafatrao manan-danja — na dia tsy afaka eo "
"ianao handefa azy ireo."

#: app/templates/index.html:17
msgid ""
"Whether you’re planning ahead, setting up emergency communication, or "
"building peace of mind, Grylli helps automate your message delivery via "
"multiple channels including email, webhooks, and Apprise notifications."
msgstr ""
"Na mikasa mialoha ianao, manomana serasera vonjy maika, na manangana "
"filaminan-tsaina, Grylli dia manampy amin'ny fanamafisana automatique ny "
"fandefasana ny hafatrao amin'ny alalan'ny mailaka, webhooks, na "
"fampahafantarana Apprise raha tsy mahazo toky ianao."

#: app/templates/index.html:19
msgid "Getting Started"
msgstr "Manomboka"

#: app/templates/index.html:21
msgid "Create a message, email, or reminder."
msgstr "Manangana hafatra na mailaka."

#: app/templates/index.html:22
msgid "Set your check-in interval and grace period (for messages)."
msgstr "Apetrakao ny elanelam-potoana handaharanao sy ny fahafahana."

#: app/templates/index.html:23
msgid "Assign one or more delivery destinations."
msgstr "Asiana toerana fandefasana iray na maromaro."

#: app/templates/index.html:24
msgid "Optionally attach files for secure emails."
msgstr ""
"Mipetrapetraha antontan-taratasy ho an'ny mailaka azo antoka raha tianao."

#: app/templates/index.html:25
msgid "Schedule reminders to send at specific times or on a recurring basis."
msgstr ""
"Mamorona fampahatsiahivana halefa amin'ny fotoana voatondro na "
"miverimberina."

#: app/templates/index.html:26
msgid "Enable the message or reminder to activate delivery."
msgstr ""
"Ampandehanana ny hafatra na ny fampahatsiahivana mba hampihetsika ny "
"fandefasana."

#: app/templates/index.html:28
msgid ""
"Regularly check in to Grylli to prevent automated delivery; miss a check-in "
"and Grylli sends your messages as scheduled."
msgstr ""
"Ataovy matetika ny fisavana ao Grylli mba hisorohana ny fandefasana mandeha "
"ho azy; raha tsy manao fisavana ianao dia alefan'i Grylli araka ny "
"fandaharam-potoana ny hafatrao."

#: app/templates/privacy.html:10
msgid "Privacy Notice"
msgstr "Fanamarihana momba ny Fiainana Manokana"

#: app/templates/privacy.html:13
msgid ""
"Grylli respects your privacy and is designed to minimize the collection and "
"storage of personal data."
msgstr ""
"Grylli manaja ny fiainanao manokana ary natao mba hampihena ny fanangonana "
"sy fitehirizana angon-drakitra manokana."

#: app/templates/privacy.html:14
msgid ""
"All data is encrypted where appropriate and remains fully under your control"
" if you self-host this platform."
msgstr ""
"Ny angon-drakitra rehetra dia voaaro amin'ny alalan'ny tsiambaratelo rehefa "
"ilaina ary mijanona eo ambany fifehezanao tanteraka raha mampiantrano "
"samirery izany sehatra izany ianao."

#: app/templates/privacy.html:17
msgid "What Data We Collect"
msgstr "Izay Angon-drakitra Angoninay"

#: app/templates/privacy.html:19
msgid "Email address and password hash (for authentication)"
msgstr "Adiresy mailaka sy hash tenimiafina (ho an'ny fankatoavana)"

#: app/templates/privacy.html:20
msgid "Optional MFA secret and recovery codes (encrypted at rest)"
msgstr ""
"Kaody MFA tsy voatery sy kaody fanarenana (voaaro ao anaty fitoeran-"
"drakitra)"

#: app/templates/privacy.html:21
msgid "Reminder and message content you configure"
msgstr "Afohezina sy votoatin’ny hafatra noforoninao"

#: app/templates/privacy.html:22
msgid "User-specific settings, SMTP configuration (if provided)"
msgstr "Fanamarinam-panokana ho an'ny mpampiasa, fanamora-na SMTP (raha misy)"

#: app/templates/privacy.html:25
msgid "How Your Data Is Used"
msgstr "Ny Fomba Ampiasain'ny Angon-drakitrao"

#: app/templates/privacy.html:27
msgid ""
"Your data is used solely for the purpose of delivering reminders and "
"messages according to your preferences."
msgstr ""
"Ny angon-drakitrao dia ampiasaina fotsiny ho an'ny tanjon'ny fandefasana "
"fifampahatsiahivana sy hafatra araka ny safidinao."

#: app/templates/privacy.html:28
msgid ""
"Grylli does not share, sell, or transmit your personal data to any third "
"parties."
msgstr ""
"Grylli dia tsy mizara, mivarotra, na mandefa ny angona-tsika ho amin'olon-"
"telo hafa."

#: app/templates/privacy.html:31
msgid "Your Rights"
msgstr "Ny Zony"

#: app/templates/privacy.html:33
msgid ""
"You can export all of your data at any time from the Account Settings page."
msgstr ""
"Azonao atao ny manondrana ny angon-drakitrao rehetra isaky ny te hivoaka "
"amin'ny Pejy Fikirana Kaonty."

#: app/templates/privacy.html:34
msgid "You may permanently delete your account and all associated data."
msgstr ""
"Tsy afaka mamafa ny kaontinao ianao satria ilay mpitantana farany ianao."

#: app/templates/privacy.html:35
msgid ""
"If you are using a self-hosted instance, contact the instance administrator "
"for data inquiries."
msgstr ""
"Raha mampiasa fizarana mampiantrano tena ianao, mifandraisa amin'ny "
"mpandrindra fizarana raha misy fanontaniana momba ny angon-drakitra."

#: app/templates/privacy.html:38
msgid "Self-Hosting Responsibility"
msgstr "Andraikitry ny Fampiantranoana Tena"

#: app/templates/privacy.html:40
msgid ""
"If you are running Grylli on your own server, you are responsible for the "
"storage, processing, and lawful handling of all user data on that instance."
msgstr ""
"Raha mampandeha Grylli amin'ny server anao ianao, tompon'andraikitra amin'ny"
" fitahirizana, fanodinana, ary fikarakarana ara-dalàna ny angon-drakitra "
"rehetra ao amin'io fizarana io ianao."

#: app/templates/privacy.html:44
msgid ""
"This notice was last updated in June 2025 and may evolve to reflect changes "
"in the software or regulatory landscape."
msgstr ""
"Ity fanamarihana ity dia noforonina tamin'ny Jona 2025 ary mety hivoatra mba"
" hifanaraka amin'ny fiovan'ny rindrambaiko na lalàna mifehy."

